# 🔹 5. FLOYD WARSHALL

### 🧠 Use When

* All pairs shortest path

### 💡 Core Idea

👉 Try every node as intermediate

### ⚙️ Algorithm

```id="a9w2lx"
for k in nodes:
    for i in nodes:
        for j in nodes:
            dist[i][j] = min(
                dist[i][j],
                dist[i][k] + dist[k][j]
            )
```

