# 🔹 6. UNION FIND (DISJOINT SET)

### 🧠 Use When

* Connected components
* Cycle detection (undirected graph)

### 💡 Core Idea

👉 Group nodes into sets

### ⚙️ Algorithm

```id="s3k8fj"
find(x):
    if parent[x] != x:
        parent[x] = find(parent[x])
    return parent[x]

union(x, y):
    px = find(x)
    py = find(y)
    if px != py:
        parent[py] = px
```

