# 🔹 9. TARJAN’S ALGORITHM

### 🧠 Use When

* Bridges / articulation points

### 💡 Core Idea

👉 Track discovery time + lowest reachable

### ⚙️ Idea (simplified)

* maintain:

  * `tin[]` (time of entry)
  * `low[]` (lowest reachable)

👉 if `low[child] > tin[node]` → bridge

